&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;LTR&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background: white;&quot;&gt;With the arrival of the Jews who had been expelled from Spain in 1492, interest in Maimonides&apos; writings declined, and the Spanish Jewish tradition of Kabbalah and mysticism started to&amp;#160;flourish. &amp;#160;By the 17&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; century the library&#8217;s contents had been dispersed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

