&lt;p class=&quot;DefaultStyle&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Born in Cordoba in 1138, Maimonides grew up during the rule of the Berberdynasty of the &lt;i&gt;Murabitun&lt;/i&gt; (Almoravids). Under their rule the Jewish and the Christian communities were protected according to Muslim law.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

