&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top: 4.8pt; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: 115%; background: white;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;The Zweigs&apos; house in Brazil was later turned into a museum and is now known as&amp;#160;Casa Stefan Zweig.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
