&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;From the smaller of the two seals on the manuscript&#8217;s front, we can surmise that the Qur&#8217;an passed into the hands of none other than the Ottoman Sultan Selim ibn Bayazid (r.1512-1520), who vanquished the Safavid Persians in the Battle of Chaldiran Valley, on the border of Persia and Azerbaijan, in August 1514, and then seized the treasures of Tabriz for his collection in Istanbul.&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

