&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;In March, 1939 Tiachiv came under Hungarian sovereignty and the Jews began to suffer from oppressive legislation. The local synagogue was sacked, and beatings and harassment became part of everyday life.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;The German army conquered Hungary on the 19th of March, 1944.&amp;#160; A ghetto was established in April, into which about 10,000 Jews from the region were deported. Each apartment in the ghetto housed 10-15 persons, no food was supplied and the population began to starve.&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Those who tried to escape were turned over to the Hungarian police who worked in cooperation with the Nazis. The Jews of the Tiachiv Ghetto were deported to Auschwitz between the 22th-26th of May, 194&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;4.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt; 
&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
