&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Dr. Shoshana Weich has been documenting Ladino music for many years. In the following film Shoshana gives an introduction (min. 00:00-07:21), followed by several recordings of Ladino songs made by her (min. 7:21-21:00). Dr. Weich deposited her collection at the National Library; the last part includes a recording of Ladino music taped at the concert &quot;Spanish &lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background: white; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;Cancionero&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt; and Romansero according to &amp;#160;the tradition of the Jews of Thessalonica &quot; &amp;#160;held at the NLI in 20.11.2013 (min.21:00-49:02).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

