&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Besides Newton&apos;s theological papers, the collection includes beautiful Books of Hours, letters from Napoleon Bonaparte, and many more important manuscripts.&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
