&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;When Sarah despairs of having a child, she gives Abraham her slave-girl so that she may bear him a child. (Genesis 16)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

