&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After defeating the rebellious kings in the Valley of Siddim Abraham (kneeling in his armour) is met by &lt;span style=&quot; color: black; background: white;&quot;&gt;Melchizedek&amp;#160;king of Shalem (the future Jerusalem) and priest to the Most High God, who offers him bread and wine and gives him a blessing.&lt;/span&gt; (Genesis 14:18-20)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

