}
--&gt;
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The Israel Collection&lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt;serves as the repository for the &apos;National memory&apos; of the State and&amp;#160;the Land of Israel. It contains all private and governmental material published in Israel, as well as ephemera, internet material, photographs, and the personal archives of prominent artists and cultural figures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

