&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;At present, the Library houses&amp;#160; over 3 million books including incunabula, manuscripts, periodicals, personal archives, music, maps, photographs and audio recordings. These are divided into four main collections: Judiaca, Israel, Islam and Humanities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

