&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;The palace of King David and above it Bathsheba, the future mother of King Solomon, bathing on the roof near the palace.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
