&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Yahuda&apos;s rich collection of Jewish manuscripts includes the most beautiful existing manuscript of Maimonides&apos; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Mishneh Torah, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;as well as various manuscripts of the Old Testament, commentaries and philological and philosophical treatises written by Jewish scholars.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

