&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;The Via Dolorosa &#8211; Jesus is commanded to carry the Cross, he falls, and is then assisted by Simon of Cyrene.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
