&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Sarah is giving birth to Isaac. The new-born baby is being held by the midwife while the maids assist Sarah. (Genesis 21:1-6).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
