&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Via Dolorosa of Jesus, from his trial to his Crucifixion is depicted in detail in Adrichom&apos;s map. &amp;#160;&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

