&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Abraham is visited by the three angels. While offering them a place to rest and water to wash&amp;#160; their feet, he is given the surprising tidings that he and Sarah will soon have a child. Sarah is seen in the background preparing the calf. (Genesis 18)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt; 
