}
p {
margin-top: 0pt;  margin-bottom: 0pt;
}
--&gt;
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After returning to Canaan from Egypt Abraham builds an altar in Beth-El where God appeared to him and promised to give the land to him and to his descendants. (Genesis 13:1-12)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt; 
