&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;This is the story of the fascinating journey of a Torah scroll. The scroll was written in Spain in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;the 14th or 15th century. It&amp;#160;travelled to Rhodes with the Jewish exiles from Spain, was hidden during the Nazi occupation in a Muslim mosque, and was finally brought to the National Library of Israel by descendants of the community of Rhodes in 1999. &amp;#160;&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

