&lt;p dir=&quot;LTR&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Written between 1300-1350 in Spain, this is the most splendid illuminated copy known. Although copied in Spain, most of the illustrations were done in Perugia, Italy around 1400, in the studio of Matteo di Ser Camb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;io.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

