&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; background: white;&quot;&gt;The Mishnah Commentary remained in the hands of the family in Aleppo along with other precious manuscripts for several generations. &amp;#160;The family encouraged the Jews in Aleppo to make authorized copies of the manuscripts in the library.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt; 
