&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top: 5.05pt; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 1.45pt; margin-left: 8.65pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;After the war, the scroll was returned to the few survivors of the community. The honorary president of the community, Mr. Moshe Sauriano gave it to the Benatar family, to be brought to the National Library, in memory of the Jews of Rhodes who were killed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
